\f1\b Energy
\f0\b0  Division loan specialists will be on hand both days to assist people interested in 4 percent loans to pay for 
\f1\b renewable
\f0\b0  
\f1\b energy
\f0\b0  projects. \
Up to 100 diesel vehicle owners will get to try five gallons of free B20 biodiesel fuel provided by BriCo of Idaho. \
