\f1\b Energy
\f0\b0  Division. A Trans IV bus which runs on B20 biodiesel will be on display at the fair. Trans IV operates more than 30 of its vehicles on B20 as part of the B20 Magic Valley program, the 
\f1\b Energy
\f0\b0  Division's statement said. \
The Idaho Mustard Bug, a Volkswagen Beetle that runs on 100 percent Idaho-grown mustard seed oil, will be on display. Magic Valley Honda and Toyota dealers will also display hybrid vehicle sedans that combine gasoline and electric power to get up to 50 miles to the gallon, the 
\f1\b Energy
\f0\b0  Division said. \
